gwt.g2d.client.math
Class Matrix

java.lang.Object
  gwt.g2d.client.math.Matrix

public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a 3x3 matrix for 2D transformation. The matrix has the following structure: 

 m11 m21 dx
 m12 m22 dy
  0   0   1

Author:
hao1300@gmail.com
